Ndepụta Flora Rare na Ibu ụzọ Flora bụ usoro nke a na enye ihe ọkụkụ nchekwa nke Western Australia ụzọ
Gọọmentị nke Western Australia's Ngalaba gburugburu na nchekwa mepụtara ya, e ji ya mee ihe nke ukwuu n'ime ngalaba ahụ, gụnyere Western Australian Herbarium

Akwụkwọ akụkọ herbarium, Nuytsia, nke bipụtara ihe karịrị otu ụzọ n'ụzọ anọ nke akwụkwọ nchekwa nke steeti ahụ, chọrọ ka a tinye ọnọdụ nchekwa na mbipụta niile nke akwụkwọ ọhụrụ nke Western Australia nke yiri ka ọ dị ụkọ ma ọ bụ na eyi egwu.
